     <p><%= icon('warning-sign') %> The <i>name</i> of the package has to represents the package contents. In particular it has to obey the following rules: <u>lower case letters only</u>, <u>no spaces or special characters as accented letters,  &, /, ?, ...</u> except . (dot), the - (minus sign), the + (plus sign) and numbers. Some examples of valid names for the Operating Systems course are: operatingsystems2012, operatingsystems, so-slide, so-exercise1, so+workers.</p>
 <p><%= icon('info-sign') %> The <i>description</i> of the package should be a self explanatory summary of the package contents.</p>
